✅ Steps for file creation & linking (short):

1️⃣ Create config file:
/etc/nginx/sites-available/your_config.conf

2️⃣ Add your server block (like the one you wrote).

3️⃣ Link it:
ln -s /etc/nginx/sites-available/your_config.conf /etc/nginx/sites-enabled/

4️⃣ Test config:
nginx -t

5️⃣ Reload NGINX:
nginx -s reload
